## Usage

To use this software, either refer directly to the executable aplt in
the bin-directory or make sure that the bin-directory is mentioned in
your PATH environment variable.

See the web page https://github.com/melsman/apltail for general
information about the usage of the system. The lib/apltail directory
contains the prelude.apl file and the share/apltail/tests/ directory
contains APL test files.

## Running the tests

To run the tests in the tests/ directory, execute the following
commands:

   $ cd tests/
   $ APLT=../../../bin/aplt PRELUDE=../../../lib/apltail/prelude.apl make test

